---
title: Swedish Pork Meatballs & Bacon Sauce with Garlicky Greens & Cheesy Mash
description: We’ve given our go-to meatballs a Swedish-inspired twist by topping them with a creamy sauce that’s so good, everyone will
be asking you how you made it. Serve with a Parmesan-laced mash and almond-adorned garlicky greens for the ultimate
crowd-pleaser!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6769138d9bfc6de73c8e4709-259d3821.jpeg
